history.content:
Join us to present to the CA State Controller Betty Yee, eat free food, and create for $5000+ in prizes! In this hybrid hackathon, we pride ourselves in helping both our guided beginner teams and experienced hackers explore technology, develop their skills, and support social good in tech culture. This event is open people of ALL backgrounds. 

Sign up as a participant at tinyurl.com/fa21civhacks or as a mentor (receive free meals & a $20 gift card as a token of appreciation) for beginner teams at tinyurl.com/civhacksmentor! 

If you have any questions or concerns, please email eavpvotecoalition@asuc.org! We're looking forward to see you soon :)
history.subject: ASUC x AWE presents CivHacks (11/13-11/14): Sign Up Today!
